contentBody: Which is even number ? ( This is example for Multiple Choice Single Choice )
answerExplanation: An even number is divisible by 2. Among the given options only two is divisible by 2.

contentBody: Which is odd number ? ( This is example for Multiple Choice Multi Choice )
answerExplanation: Odd numbers are not divisible by 2. One and three are odd numbers as they leave a remainder when divided by 2.

contentBody: What is your name? ( This is example for Subjective type input question )
answerExplanation: This is a basic identification question to collect the candidate's name.
